==Tatar==
===Etymology===
From tatar хары - hoary. Akin to Old English [[har#Old English|hār]] - [[hoar#English|hoar]], Middle English hor - [[hoar#English|hoar]]

#''Etymological latin spelling: hoar'd''
#''Phonetic latin spelling: hart''
===Noun===
'''харт'''
#hoared, old person; [[hoary#English|hoary]]; white or gray with age;

=== Adjective ===
#[[old]]; [[hoary]]

